00:00:00.008 --> 00:00:04.950
 MainActivity.java faylida 
 MainActivity decrement metodiga o‘zgartiramiz.

00:00:04.950 --> 00:00:07.640
Avvalo, integer 
o‘zgaruvchisini yaratamiz 

00:00:07.640 --> 00:00:09.300
va qiymatni ikki bilan boshlaymiz.

00:00:09.300 --> 00:00:13.680
Keyin miqdor o‘zgaruvchisini joriy qiymatiga

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:15.020
teng bo‘lishi uchun yangilaymiz.

00:00:15.020 --> 00:00:18.820
Bunday holda, miqdorning joriy qiymati ikki,

00:00:18.820 --> 00:00:20.820
va natijada ikki minus bir birga teng.

00:00:20.820 --> 00:00:23.910
So‘ngra, miqdorni ko‘rsatganimizda, 
u bir qiymatga ega bo‘lishi kerak.

00:00:23.910 --> 00:00:27.730
Men minus tugmachasini bosganimda, 
qiymatni birga yangilaydi.

00:00:27.730 --> 00:00:30.710
 Breakpoint ni qo‘shib, ilovani 
debug rejimida ishga tushirishim mumkin.

00:00:30.710 --> 00:00:33.960
Minus tugmachasini bossam, 
breakpoint ishga tushadi.

00:00:33.960 --> 00:00:37.230
Bosqichni davom ettirsak bo‘ladi, keyin 

00:00:37.230 --> 00:00:39.390
o‘zgaruvchining miqdori 
ikkiligini darhol ko‘raman.

00:00:39.390 --> 00:00:42.770
Yana bir marta bosilsa, soni bittaga kamaydi, 

00:00:42.770 --> 00:00:44.390
endi esa ularning soni bittaga teng.

00:00:44.390 --> 00:00:47.590
Agar men reseume ga bossam, 
u holda ekran yangilanadi.

00:00:48.780 --> 00:00:49.540
Ajoyib.

00:00:49.540 --> 00:00:52.080
Endi barcha kichik qismlar joyida.

00:00:52.080 --> 00:00:55.280
Keyingi videoda biz miqdorni 
tanlagichni bir necha marta 

00:00:55.280 --> 00:00:57.130
bosganingizda ishlaydigan 
qilib ulashni tugatamiz.

